%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20such%20a%20great%20bunch%20of%20players%20and%20staff%20here%20that%20we%20all%20know%20what%20everyone%20is%20about%20and%20how%20we%20are%20going%20to%20go%20about%20it%2C%20and%20for%20me%2C%20that's%20more%20important%20than%20anything%20else.%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20please%20everyone%20and%20everyone's%20got%20opinions%2C%20but%20they%20aren't%20facts%2C%20they're%20opinions%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECummins%20believes%20he%20will%20step%20down%20as%20captain%20before%20retiring%20as%20a%20player%2C%20but%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20do%20so%20anytime%20soon.%20In%20the%20fourth%20Test%2C%20the%20right-arm%20pacer%20similarly%20struggled%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20taking%20only%20one%20wicket%20and%20allowing%20129%20runs%20in%2023%20overs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20it%20does%20have%20a%20shelf%20life.%20I%20won't%20put%20a%20date%20on%20it%2C%20I've%20got%20to%20get%20there%20first.%20I%20feel%20like%20every%20Test%20match%20I%20learn%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%20you%20just%20get%20exposed%20to%20more%20things%20with%20each%20game.%20I'm%20loving%20working%20with%20this%20team%20and%20the%20staff.%20Enjoying%20it%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20we'll%20see%20what%20the%20future%20holds.%20I%20feel%20like%20with%20each%20game%20I'm%20getting%20better%20and%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20fair%20bit%20more%20left%20in%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cummins%20said%20of%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Australia%20has%20already%20retained%20the%20urn%2C%20captain%20Cummins%20insisted%20that%20his%20team%20is%20still%20very%20eager%20to%20win%20the%20long-awaited%20Ashes%20series%20in%20England.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20think%20it's%20shifted%20too%20much%20over%20the%20series%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%20I%20think%20Edgbaston%20again%2C%20was%20another%20moment%20where%20there%20wasn't%20a%20lot%20in%20it%20(the%20pitch)%20for%20the%20bowlers.%20They%20scored%20almost%20400%