n-bites-4244269%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%2C%20Google%20and%20Other%20AI%20Leaders%20Set%20Up%20Industry%20Watchdog%20to%20Ensure%20'Safety'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F06142516%2FUntitled-design-19.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Four%20technology%20companies%20researching%20artificial%20intelligence%20%E2%80%93%20Anthropic%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%93%20have%20announced%20an%20industry%20body%20which%20shall%20act%20as%20a%20watchdog%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20responsibility%20as%20AI%20models%20are%20being%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Microsoft%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.microsoft.com%2Fon-the-issues%2F2023%2F07%2F26%2Fanthropic-google-microsoft-openai-launch-frontier-model-forum%2F%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20body%2C%20called%20the%20Frontier%20Model%20Forum%2C%20is%20going%20to%20draw%20on%20the%20technical%20and%20operational%20expertise%20of%20its%20member%20companies%20to%20benefit%20the%20entire%20AI%20ecosystem.%20The%20group%20will%20focus%20on%20technical%20evaluations%20and%20will%20set%20benchmarks.%20It%20will%20also%20develop%20a%20public%20library%20of%20solutions%20to%20support%20best%20practices%20and%20standards%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20notes%3A%20%E2%80%9CGovernments%20and%20industry%20agree%20that%2C%20while%20AI%20offers%20tremendous%20promise%20to%20benefit%20the%20world%2C%20appropriate%20guardrails%20are%20required%20to%20mitigate%20risks.%20Important%20contributions%20to%20these%20efforts%20have%20already%20been%20made%20by%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20governments%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20the%20OECD%2C%20the%20G7%20(via%20the%20Hiroshima%20AI%20process)%2C%20and%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20body%20that%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20mitigating%20AI%E2%80%99s%20risks%2C%20the%20Fron