22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singer%20Sinead%20O'Connor%2C%20Lifelong%20Non-Conformist%2C%20Passes%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27104027%2FUntitled-design-19-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAcclaimed%20artiste%20Sinead%20O%E2%80%99Connor%20has%20passed%20away%20at%20the%20age%20of%2056.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20cited%20by%20Irish%20broadcaster%20RTE%2C%20the%20singer%E2%80%99s%20family%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20with%20great%20sadness%20that%20we%20announce%20the%20passing%20of%20our%20beloved%20Sinead.%20Her%20family%20and%20friends%20are%20devastated%20and%20have%20requested%20privacy%20at%20this%20very%20difficult%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO%E2%80%99Connor%20was%20propelled%20to%20worldwide%20fame%20by%20the%20Prince%20cover%20%E2%80%98Nothing%20Compares%202%20U%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20won%20the%201990%20Billboard%20Music%20Awards%20for%20Best%20Single%20in%20the%20World.%20The%20string-accompanied%20ballad%20topped%20the%20music%20charts%20from%20Europe%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20already%20received%20critical%20acclaim%20for%20her%20first%20album%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lion%20and%20the%20Cobra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20featuring%20her%20debut%20hit%20%E2%80%98Mandinka.%E2%80%99%20The%20singer%20released%2010%20studio%20albums%20in%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReaction%20to%20singer%E2%80%99s%20passing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20political%20figures%20and%20celebrities%20have%20been%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20singer%2C%20with%20Ireland%E2%80%99s%20President%20Michael%20D.Higgins%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20Ireland%20has%20lost%20at%20such%20a%20relatively%20young%20age%20is%20one%20of%20our%20greatest%20and%20most%20gifted%20composers%2C%20songwriters%20and%20performers%20of%20recent%20decades%2C%20one%20who%20had%20a%20unique%20talent%20and%20extraordinary%20connection%20with%20her%20audience%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20held%20such%20love%20and%20warmth%20for%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIreland%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Leo%20Varadkar%20said%20O%E2%80%99Connor%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmusic%20was%20loved%20around%20the%20world%20and%20her%20talent%20was%20unmatched%20and%20beyond%20compare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrish%20former%20UFC%20champion%20Conor%20McGregor%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20has%20lost%20an%20artist%20with%20the%20voice%20of%20an%20angel.%20Ireland%20has%20lost%20an%20iconic%20voice%20and%20one%20of%20our%20absolute%20finest%2C%20by%20a%20long%20shot.%20And%20I%20have%20lost%20a%20friend.%20Sinead%E2%80%99s%20music%20will%20live%20on%20and%20continue%20to%20inspire!%20Rest%20In%20Peace%2C%20Sinead%20you%20are%20home%20with%20your%20son%20I%20am%20sure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO%E2%80%99Connor%20had%20performed%20a%20stirring%20rendition%20of%20%E2%80%98Foggy%20dew%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20entrance%20of%20McGregor%20before%20one%20of%20his%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinger%20Tori%20Amos%20was%20among%20the%20musicians%20paying%20tribute%20and%20called%20her%20%E2%80%9Ca%20force%20of%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20passion%2C%20such%20intense%20presence%20and%20a%20beautiful%20soul%2C%20who%20battled%20her%20own%20personal%20demons%20courageously%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amos%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBe%20at%20peace%20dear%20Sinead%2C%20you%20will%20forever%20be%20in%20our%20hearts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F309626%2Fshehla-rashid-muslim-hindutva-congress%2F%5C%22%3ESinead%20O%E2%80%99Connor%2C%20Shehla%20Rashid%20and%20the%20Only%20%E2%80%98Good%20Muslims%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVociferous%20in%20social%20and%20political%20views%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20artiste%20kept%20her%20head%20shaved%20in%20what%20she%20said%20was%20a%20response%20to%20music%20company%20bosses%20pressurising%20her%20to%20be%20conventionally%20glamorous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutspoken%20in%20her%20social%20and%20political%20views%20and%20regularly%20stirring%20up%20controversy%2C%20O%E2%80%99Connor%20was%20a%20lifelong%20non-conformist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20child%20%E2%80%9Ckleptomaniac%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20arrested%20several%20times%20before%20she%20was%20eventually%20sent%20to%20a%20church-run%20training%20facility%20where%20a%20sympathetic%20nun%20encouraged%20her%20to%20pursue%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20suppose%20I%E2%80%99ve%20got%20to%20say%20that%20music%20saved%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%202013.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20either%20jail%20or%20music.%20I%20got%20lucky.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO%E2%80%99Connor%20was%20a%20critic%20of%20the%20Catholic%20Church%20long%20before%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20were%20widely%20reported%20and%20made%20headlines%20by%20tearing%20up%20a%20photo%20of%20Pope%20John%20Paul%20II%20in%20October%201992%20while%20appearing%20on%20live%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pope%20Benedict%20XVI%20apologised%20to%20Ireland%20in%202010%20to%20atone%20for%20decades%20of%20abuse%2C%20O%E2%80%99Connor%20condemned%20the%20apology%20saying%20it%20did%20not%20go%20far%20enough.%20She%20announced%20in%202018%20that%20she%20had%20converted%20to%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20singer%2C%20who%20married%20four%20times%2C%20had%20a%20troubled%20personal%20life.%20She%20was%20open%20about%20mental%20health%20issues%20on%20social%20media%2C%20saying%20she%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20bipolar%20disorder.%20Her%20son%2C%20Shane%2C%20died%20last%20year%20aged%2017%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO%E2%80%99Connor%20is%20survived%20by%20three%20of%20her%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsinger-sinead-oconnor-dies-aged-56%2Fa-66359082%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%