aya%20Prasad%20Thomas%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Anju%2C%20a%20married%20Indian%20woman%20who%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20meet%20her%20Facebook%20friend%20Nasrullah%20and%20got%20married%20to%20him%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20expressed%20his%20sorrow%20and%20disappointment%20at%20his%20daughter's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20as%20good%20as%20dead%20for%20the%20family.%20She%20has%20no%20right%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India.%20If%20she%20returns%2C%20then%20she%20has%20to%20face%20strict%20punishment.%20What%20she%20did%20is%20wrong%20and%20people%20who%20do%20that%20deserve%20punishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaya%20Prasad%20Thomas%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnju%2C%20a%20married%20Indian%20woman%C2%A0travelled%20to%C2%A0Pakistan's%C2%A0Khyber%C2%A0Pakhtunkhwa%20province%C2%A0and%20married%20her%20Facebook%20friend%20there%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20same%2C%20Thomas%20said%20that%20Anju%20has%20no%20right%20to%20take%20her%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20respectable%20country%20and%20I'm%20ashamed%20of%20what%20she%20did%20and%20apologised%20to%20the%20government.%20He%20added%20that%20she%20doesn't%20have%20any%20right%20to%20take%20her%20two%20children.%20Don't%20let%20her%20touch%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHer%20action%20and%20name%20are%20a%20taint%20on%20us%20therefore%20I%20requested%20to%20remove%20my%20name%20from%20my%20daughter's%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rerun%20of%20Seema%20Haider's%20case%2C%20Anju%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20allegedly%20crossed%20over%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20meet%20her%20lover.%20The%20woman%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Bhiwadi%20and%20married%20with%20two%20kids.%20However%2C%20unlike%20Seema%2C%20Anju%20was%20granted%20entry%20into%20Pakistan%20by%20the%20authorities%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20any%20relations%20with%20her%20(Anju).%20The%20moment%20she%20left%20India%2C%20we%20cut%20off%20all%20ties%20with%20her.%20I%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20my%20daughter%20could%20do%20something%20like%20this.%20What%20she%20has%20done%20is%20very%20shameful%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gaya%20Prasad%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnju's%20husband--%20Arvind%20Kumar%20said%20that%20before%20leaving%2C%20his%20wife%20told%20him%20that%20she%20is%20visiting%20one%20of%20her%20friends%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20voice%20call%20last%20night%2C%20she%20said%20that%20I%20am%20in%20Lahore.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20why%20she%20went%20to%20Lahore%20and%20how%20she%20got%20the%20visa%20and%20other%20stuff.%20She%20informed%20me%20that%20she%20will%20return%20within%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumar%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Police%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20initiated%20a%20preliminary%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Bhiwadi%20ASP%20Sujit%20Shankar%2C%20prima%20facie%20indicates%20that%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20love%20affair.%20The%20police%20official%20also%20added%20that%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20Anju%20if%20any%20fake%20document%20is%20used%20to%20cross%20the%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrima%20facie%2C%20this%20can%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20love%20affair%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20say%20anything%20until%20concrete%20evidence%20is%20found.%20We%20will%20not%20take%20any%20formal%20investigation%20since%20no%20complaint%20has%20been%20received.%20There%20are%20acts%20like%20the%20Passport%20Act%20and%20others%2C%20action%20can%20be%20taken%20against%20her%20if%20any%20fake%20document%20has%20been%20used%20to%20cross%20over.%20All%20angles%20will%20be%20investigated%20if%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20H