%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%20%26quot%3BMillions%20of%20Jews%20were%20brutally%20murdered%20in%20execution%20sites%20...%20with%20entire%20communities%20wiped%20out%20regardless%20of%20their%20usefulness%20or%20contributions%20to%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20skilled%20or%20useful%20did%20not%20spare%20them%20from%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20gas%20chambers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20avoid%20such%20oversimplifications%20in%20talking%20about%20this%20complex%20tragic%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Auschwitz%20Memorial%20concluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94Auschwitz%20Memorial%20(%40AuschwitzMuseum)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1683710180448411649%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20the%20White%20House%20strongly%20rebuked%20Gutfeld's%20comments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fmedia%2F4118997-white-house-condemns-fox-hosts-holocaust-comments%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20The%20Hill%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Fox%20News%20allowed%20to%20be%20said%20on%20their%20air%20yesterday%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20so%20far%20failed%20to%20condemn%20%E2%80%94%20is%20an%20obscenity%2C%26quot%3B%20spokesperson%20Andrew%20Bates%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20defending%20a%20horrid%2C%20dangerous%2C%20extreme%20lie%20that%20insults%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20Americans%20who%20suffered%20from%20the%20evil%20of%20enslavement%2C%20a%20Fox%20News%20host%20told%20another%20horrid%2C%20dangerous%2C%20and%20extreme%20lie%20that%20insults%20th