1271_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20President%20Says%20His%20Primary%20Aim%20Is%20To%20Discuss%2013th%20Amendment%20With%20All%20Parties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26231515%2FAll-party-leaders-meeting-03.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20asserted%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2026%2C%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20discuss%20the%2013th%20Amendment%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20a%20key%20aspect%20of%20the%201987%20Indo-Lanka%20accord%20%E2%80%93%20with%20all%20parties%20as%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20%E2%80%9Caffects%20the%20entire%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2013th%20Amendment%20called%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces%20and%20decentralisation%20of%20powers%2C%20especially%20of%20police%20and%20land.%20While%20provinces%20have%20been%20created%20with%20their%20own%20administrations%2C%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20police%20and%20land%20continued%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Colombo.%20This%20has%20created%20resentment%20among%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWickremesinghe%20held%20an%20All-Party%20Conference%20at%20the%20Presidential%20Secretariat%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20highlighted%20that%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20amendment%20should%20involve%20inputs%20from%20all%20relevant%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conference%20was%20organized%20to%20update%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20party%20leaders%20on%20the%20National%20Reconciliation%20Program%20and%20the%20North-East%20Development%20Plan%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmd.gov.lk%2Fnews%2Fprimary-aim-is-to-discuss-the-13th-amendment-of-the-constitution-with-all-parties%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20that%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20pass%20new%20laws%20to%20address%20existing%20problems%20and%20that%20power%20rests%20solely%20with%20parliament.%20He%20was%20bringing%20forth%20%E2%80%9Crelevant%20proposals%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country%2C%20but%20the%20%E2%80%9Cresponsibility%20of%20implementing%20them%20lay%20with%20all%20the%20representatives%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%20as%20he%20alone%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20achieve%20it%20with%20his%20single%20vote%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20full%20implementation%20of%20the%2013th%20Amendment.%20However%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20is%20the%20sole%20MP%20of%20his%20party%20and%20his%20presidency%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20ruling%20Sri%20Lanka%20Podujana%20Peramuna%20(SLPP)%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20opposed%20the%20decentralisation%20of%20powers.%20There%20is%20not%20much%20hope%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20the%20current%20exercise%20would%20yield%20any%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Wickremesinghe%20suggested%20that%20the%20central%20government%20should%20formulate%20policies%20for%20the%20country%2C%20while%20provincial%20councils%20should%20provide%20the%20necessary%20facilities%20for%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20development%20activities%20in%20all%20fields.%20%E2%80%9CCollaboration%20between%20all%20parties%20and%20levels%20of%20government%20was%20crucial%20for%20progress%20and%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20discussions%E2%80%9D%20among%20all%20parties%20to%20decide%20on%20granting%20police%20powers%20to%20the%20provincial%20councils%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20President%20Wickremesinghe%20proposed%20arrangements%20that%20would%20allow%20members%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Councils%20to%20concurrently%20hold%20positions%20and%20be%20appointed%20as%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20while%20members%20of%20Parliament%20could%20also%20serve%20as%20members%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Councils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Gunawardena%2C%20speaker%20Mahinda%20Yapa%20Abeywardena%2C%20opposition%20leader%20Sajith%20Premadasa%20and%20former%20president%20Maithripala%20Sirisena%20were%20among%20those%20who%20participated%20and%20expressed%20their%20views%20during%20the%20event.%20Numerous%20party%20leaders%20and%20representatives%20from%20various%20parties%20were%20also%20present%20at%20the%20occasion%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690393674000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26231515%2FAll-party-leaders-meeting-03.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-president-says-his-primary-aim-is-to-discuss-13th-amendment-with-all-parties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Amendment%2C%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%201987%20Indo-Lanka%20pact%2C%20called%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces%20and%20decentralisation%20of%20powers%2C%20especially%20of%20police%20and%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lanka-president-says-his-primary-aim-is-to-discuss-13th-amendment-with-all-parties%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sinead%20O'Connor's%20family%20'devastated'%20after%20singer%20dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690393080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-sinead-oconnor-sinead_6231308.jpg%3F20230726204658%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsinead-oconnor-dies-aged-56-irish-media-reports-12928084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Irish%20singer%20Sinead%20O'Connor%20has%20died%20aged%2056%2C%20her%20family%20has%20confirmed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29329%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3