20the%20dock%20when%20the%20jury%20announced%20its%20verdict.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20he%20mouthed%20%E2%80%9Cthank%20you%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20nine%20men%20and%20three%20woman%20jurors%2C%20before%20wiping%20away%20his%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20verdict%2C%20Spacey%20said%20he%20had%20been%20humbled%20by%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20imagine%20that%20many%20of%20you%20can%20understand%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20for%20me%20to%20process%20after%20what%20has%20just%20happened%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0reporters%20outside%20court.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20am%20humbled%20by%20the%20outcome%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpacey%20faced%20nine%20charges%2C%20including%20sexual%20assault%2C%20indecent%20assault%2C%20and%20causing%20a%20person%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20activity%20without%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20during%20the%20trial%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20four-week%20trial%20at%20Southwark%20Crown%20Court%2C%20prosecutors%20told%20jurors%20that%20the%20actor%20had%20aggressively%20groped%20three%20of%20the%20men.%20The%20fourth%20man%20said%20Spacey%20performed%20oral%20sex%20on%20him%20while%20he%20was%20passed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%2012%20hours%20of%20deliberations%2C%C2%A0the%20jurors%20reached%20majority%20decisions%20on%20the%20nine%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%C2%A0in%20London%20came%20after%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fkevin-spacey-new-york-jury-says-actor-not-liable-in-sexual-assault-case%2Fa-63513034%5C%22%3EUS%20court%20last%20year%20dismissed%20separate%20sexual%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20civil%20case%20against%20the%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20London%20trial%2C%20prosecutor%20Christine%20Agnew%20told%20jurors%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fkevin-spacey-is-