0History%20of%20No-Confidence%20Motions%2C%20as%20Modi%20Government%20Faces%20Its%20Second%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKharge%20writes%20to%20Shah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20Kharge%20also%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20saying%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20comparing%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20to%20the%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20and%20East%20India%20Company%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20single%20day%2C%20the%20respected%20Prime%20Minister%20connects%20the%20opposition%20parties%20of%20the%20country%20with%20the%20British%20rulers%20and%20the%20terrorist%20group%20and%20on%20the%20same%20day%20the%20Home%20Minister%20writes%20an%20emotional%20letter%20and%20expects%20a%20positive%20attitude%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20sharing%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20letter%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20was%20referring%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-shah-writes-manipur-opposition-mps-pm-statement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20letter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20the%20leaders%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20both%20houses%20urging%20for%20cooperation%20for%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20only%20absurd%20but%20also%20unfortunate%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20call%20the%20opposition%20parties%20directionless%20on%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20urging%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20come%20to%20the%20House%20and%20give%20a%20statement%20on%20Manipur%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20that%20doing%20so%20is%20hurting%20his%20honour.%20We%20have%20a