%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20shrine%20of%20Mata%20Chandi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20manifestations%20of%20Goddess%20Durga%2C%20is%20located%20in%20the%20high%20mountains%20of%20Kishtwar.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20of%20the%20civil%20subordinate%20judge%20in%20Kishtwar%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025%2C%20ordered%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20rights%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20land%2C%20have%20been%20compromised%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20which%2C%20the%20court%20observed%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbent%20upon%E2%80%9D%20occupying%20the%20proprietary%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20Prithvi%20Raj%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Machail%20Padder%20village%20after%20the%20two%20Delhi-based%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20Himalayan%20Heli%20Services%20Pvt%20Ltd%20and%20Aryan%20Aviation%20Pvt%20Ltd%20%E2%80%93%20occupied%20his%20land%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20despite%20his%20objection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petitioner%2C%20his%20land%20measuring%20six%20kanal%20and%20two%20marlas%20at%20Mouza%20locality%20of%20Machail%20Paddar%20was%20forcibly%20taken%20over%20and%20the%20two%20companies%20started%20levelling%20the%20ground%20for%20constructing%20the%20helipad%2C%20allegedly%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20approached%20the%20administration%20for%20justice%20but%20instead%20of%20helping%20me%2C%20they%20sided%20with%20the%20two%20companies%20and%20started%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20use%20as%20a%20helipad%20without%20my%20consent%20or%20paying%20any%20rent%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheikh%20Nasir%2C%20the%20counsel%20of%20Raj%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20quoting%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasir%20said%20that%20despite%20being%20shown%20the%20cold%20shoulder%20by%20the%20administration%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20land%20continued%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20two%20companies%20repeatedly%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%20and%20requested%20them%20to%20vacate%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20companies%2C%20who%20seem%20to%20be%20well-connected%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20any%20heed%20to%20his%20requests.%20Even%20the%20administration%20officials%20advised%20him%20not%20to%20make%20this%20an%20issue%20as%20it%20was%20connected%20to%20a%20sacred%20pilgrimage%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nasir%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Raj%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20two%20companies%20again%20tried%20to%20level%20the%20land%20forcibly%20last%20week%20but%20they%20were%20stopped%20due%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctimely%20intervention%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20neighbours%20and%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20every%20apprehension%20that%20they%20(the%20administration%20and%20aviation%20companies)%20will%20forcibly%20trespass%20and%20make%20the%20use%20of%20suit%20land%2C%20hence%20the%20cause%20of%20action%20has%20accrued%20to%20the%20plaintiff%20in%20filing%20the%20present%20suit%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuling%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20land%20owner%2C%20the%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbalance%20of%20convenience%20tilts%20in%20favour%20of%20applicant%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20stage%20if%20the%20interim%20injunction%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20not%20granted%2C%20there%20is%20every%20likelihood%20%5Bthat%20the%20land%20owner%20will%5D%20suffer%20irreparable%20loss%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20%5Bthe%20two%20companies%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20ruled%2C%20while%20asking%20the%20companies%20and%20the%20administration%20to%20vacate%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Himalayan%20Heli%20Services%20Pvt%20Ltd%20and%20Aryan%20Aviation%20Pvt%20Ltd%20for%20their%20comment.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20their%20response%20is%20received.%20The%20divisional%20commissioner%20(Jammu)%20Ramesh%20Kumar%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20his%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treacherous%20pilgrimage%20in%20Kishtwar%20to%20the%20high-altitude%20Himalayan%20shrine%20of%20Mata%20Chandi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20manifestations%20of%20Goddess%20Durga%2C%20is%20undertaken%20by%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20pilgrims%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2043-day%20pilgrimage%20started%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20arduous%2C%2030-km%20trek%20from%20Gulabgarh%20to%20Machail%20passes%20along%20the%20high%20mountains%20of%20Kishtwar%2C%20which%20are%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20finest%20and%20most-precious%20sapphires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20pilgrimages%20to%20Amarnath%20and%20Mata%20Vaishno%20Devi%20shrines%2C%20the%20Machail%20yatra%20is%20not%20managed%20by%20any%20independent%20board.%20The%20administration%20has%20set%20up%20the%20Machail%20Maata%20Yatra%20Management%20Committee%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%20of%20Jammu%2C%20while%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Kishtwar%20is%20the%20vice-chairman%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20spokesperson%2C%20the%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20Jammu%2C%20Mukesh%20Singh%2C%20the%20deputy%20inspector%20general%20of%20Doda-Kishtwar-Ramban%20range%2C%20Sunil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Kishtwar%20Devansh%20Yadav%20paid%20obeisance%20at%20the%20shrine%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM-300x192.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM-1024x655.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EADGP%20Jammu%20Mukesh%20Singh%20and%20DC%20Kishtwar%20Devansh%20Yadav%20paid%20obeisance%20at%20the%20shrine%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%20using%20the%20controversial%20helicopter%20service.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20all%20the%20senior%20officials%20visited%20the%20shrine%20by%20using%20the%20controversial%20helicopter%20service%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20on%20the%20yatra%E2%80%99s%20route%20some%20ten%20years%20ago.%20A%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20Kishtwar%20administration%20said%20that%20the%20contract%20for%20heli-service%20is%20awarded%20to%20private%20companies%20through%20a%20competitive%20bidding%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20helipads%20along%20the%20route%20to%20the%20sacred%20temple.%20One%20is%20in%20Gulabgarh%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20government%20while%20the%20second%20helipad%20is%20located%20near%20Machail%20shrine%20which%20has%20been%20built%20on%20private%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said%2C%20wishing%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20operator%20charges%20Rs%203%2C790%20per%20pilgrim%20and%20eight%20pilgrims%20are%20ferried%20to%20the%20shrine%20in%20one%20sortie.%20A%20minimum%20of%2040%20sorties%20are%20carried%20out%20per%20day.%20If%20the%20government%20charges%20Rs%2050%20for%20car%20parking%2C%20the%20denial%20of%20rent%20to%20my%20client%20is%20a%20travesty%20of%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nasir%2C%20the%20advocate%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690384027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195505%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.51.17-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-admin-forcibly-occupying-private-land-helipad-pilgrimage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Jammu%20court%20ordered%20the%20administration%2C%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20to%20vacate%20the%20land%20which%20was%20being%20used%20to%20operate%20a%20helipad%20by%20two%20private%20aviation%20players%20for%20ferrying%20pilgrims%20to%20the%20temple%20of%20Mata%20Chandi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-admin-forcibly-occupying-private-land-helipad-pilgrimage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deadly%20wildfires%20in%20Greece%20and%20other%20European%20countries%20destroy%20homes%2C%20threaten%20nature%20reserves%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690383957000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102145986%2Cimgsize-1355869.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fdeadly-wildfires-in-greece-and-other-european-countries-destroy-homes-threaten-nature-reserves%2Farticleshow%2F102145873.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102145873.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMajor%20fires%20raging%20in%20Greece%20and%20other%20European%20countries%20advanced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20causing%20additional%20deaths%2C%20destroying%20homes%20and%20threatening%20nature%20reserves%20during%20a%20third%20successive%20wave%20of%20extreme%20temperatures.%20The%20summer%20wildfires%20have%20struck%20countries%20across%20the%20region%2C%20prompting%20the%20European%20Union%20to%20expand%20its%20support%2C%20sending%20two%20Spanish%20firefighting%20planes%20to%20Tunisia%20after%20wildfires%20in%20neighboring%20Algeria%20left%20at%20least%2034%20people%20dead%20in%20recent%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fdeadly-wildfires-in-greece-and-other-european-countries-destroy-homes-threaten-nature-reserves%2Farticleshow%2F102145873.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fdeadly-wildfires-in-greece-and-other-european-countries-destroy-homes-threaten-nature-reserves%2Famp_articleshow%2F102145873.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fdeadly-wildfires-in-greece-and-other-european-countries-destroy-homes-threaten-nature-reserves%2Famp_articleshow%2F102145873.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Entrepreneur%20Flies%20Jet%2C%20Drives%20Exotic%20Cars%20But%20Says%20She%20Is%20%5C%22Struggling%5C%22%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20wildly%20successful%20serial%20entrepreneur%20Jessica%20Mah%20is%20best%20known%20as%20the%20founder%20of%20inDinero%2C%20a%20fintech%20company%20that%20helps%20small%20businesses%20to%20manage%20their%20finances.%20Ms%20Mah%20built%20her%20first%20six-figure%20business%20while%20she%20was%20in%20middle%20school%20and%20has%20since%20grown%20her%20portfolio%20of%20companies%20to%20over%20%24500%20million%20in%20value.%20The%20venture%20capitalist%20is%20a%20Forbes%2030%20Under%2030%20superstar%2C%20and%20for%20fun%2C%20she%20flies%20jet%20aircraft%20and%20drives%20exotic%20cars.%20However%2C%20she%20still%20insists%20that%20her%20life%20is%20not%20the%20fairy%20tale%20it%20appears%20to%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20LinkedIn%2C%20the%20startup%20founder%20revealed%20that%20she%20has%20dated%20celebrities%20and%20been%20on%20magazine%20covers%20but%20she%20still%20sees%20herself%20as%20a%20struggling%20entrepreneur.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20hang%20out%20with%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20in%20college%2C%20they%20say%20they%20want%20my%20life.%20But%20my%20best%20friends%20who%20know%20me%20best%20almost%20always%20say%20they%20would%20HATE%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7087840438300065792%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221337%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mah%20gave%20a%20sneak%20peek%20into%20her%20day-to-day%20life%20and%20revealed%20that%20she%20works%20all%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3B60%20hours%20would%20be%20the%20minimum%20in%20any%20given%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20serial%20entrepreneur%20also%20said%20that%20suffers%20from%20accomplishment%20dysmorphia.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20see%20my%20accomplishments%20in%20the%20esteemed%20way%20that%20many%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20US-based%20entrepreneur%20revealed%20that%20she%20is%20struggling%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20death%20of%20her%20ex-boyfriend%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20having%20trouble%20bringing%20myself%20to%20date%20again%20for%20obvious%20reasons%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mah%20acknowledged%20that%20one%20of%20her%20biggest%20problems%20is%20comparing%20herself%20to%20others.%20She%20admitted%20that%20she%20surrounds%20herself%20with%20highly%20successful%20people%20who%20have%20accomplished%20far%20more%20than%20she%20has%2C%20and%20whose%20net%20worth%20is%20higher%20than%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComparison%20is%20the%20thief%20of%20joy.%20I've%20learned%20that%20the%20hard%20way.%20But%20with%20a%20little%20trick%20I%20picked%20up%20in%20therapy%2C%20I%20find%20that%20I%20am%20comparing%20myself%20to%20others%20less%20and%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20the%20trick%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bthink%20about%20the%20bigger%20picture%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20someone%20who%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20better%20lifestyle%20than%20you%2C%20think%20about%20the%20bigger%20picture.%20Would%20you%20truly%20trade%20places%20with%20them%3F%20If%20you%20compare%20yourself%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20you%20have%20to%20compare%20yourself%20to%20ALL%20of%20their%20struggles%2C%20too.%20And%20nobody%20is%20posting%20their%20insecurities%20and%20private%20challenges%20in%20the%20open%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20am!%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20remember%20to%20view%20those%20we%20envy%20with%20a%20wider%20lens%2C%20it's%20much%20easier%20to%20see%20that%20we%20are%20all%20flawed%20and%20come%20with%20our%20own%20sets%20of%20struggles%20and%20wins.%20Yours%20is%20likely%20no%20greater%20or%20worse%20than%20all%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Mah%20concluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbring-my-daughter-back-mother-of-hyderabad-woman-who-was-found-starving-on-us-street-4241540%5C%22%3E''Bring%20My%20Daughter%20Back''%3A%20Mother%20Of%20Hyderabad%20Woman%20Who%20Was%20Found%20Starving%20On%20US%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20her%20LinkedIn%20post%20has%20divided%20opinion%20on%20social%20media.%20While%20some%20applauded%20the%20entrepreneur%20for%20writing%20about%20her%20struggles%2C%20others%20said%20she%20failed%20to%20acknowledge%20her%20own%20privilege.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20appreciate%20these%20posts%20and%20reminders.%20Especially%20the%20issue%20around%20comparison%2C%20which%20is%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%26quot%3B%