%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26180437%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-26T180423.594.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EDays%20after%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20told%20judges%20not%20to%20view%20%E2%80%98protocol%20facilities%E2%80%99%20they%20get%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjudge-explanation-railways-cji-chandrachud-displeasure%5C%22%3Emanifestation%20of%20power%20or%20authority%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20an%20instance%20of%20a%20high%20court%20judge%20using%20his%20position%20to%20call%20for%20the%20suspension%20of%20police%20officers%20surfaced%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gaurang%20Kanth%20%E2%80%93%20now%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20%E2%80%93%20wrote%20to%20the%20Delhi%20joint%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(security)%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20June%2012%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%E2%80%9D%20suspend%20police%20officials%20who%20were%20posted%20at%20his%20residence.%20Justice%20Kanth%20alleged%20that%20due%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cincompetence%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20officers%20providing%20security%20at%20his%20official%20bungalow%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20pet%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20this%20letter%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20pain%20and%20anguish.%20Due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20devotion%20and%20incompetence%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20officers%20providing%20security%20at%20my%20official%20bungalow%2C%20I%20lost%20my%20pet%20dog.%20In%20spite%20of%20repeatedly%20telling%20them%20to%20keep%20the%20door%20locked%2C%20the%20security%20officials%20deputed%20at%20my%20residence%20have%20failed%20to%20comply%20with%20my%20directions%20and%20carry%20out%20their%20professional%20duty.%20Such%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20and%20incompetence%20needs%20immediate%20attention%20as%20the%20same%20can%20cause%20grave%20danger%20to%20my%20life%20and%20liberty%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Justice%20Kanth%20whilst%20he%20was%20serving%20at%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court.%20He%20was%20transferred%20to%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20on%20July%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EJudge%20seeks%20suspension%20of%20police%20officers%20who%20failed%20to%20keep%20the%20door%20of%20his%20residence%20locked%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20pet%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEx-Delhi%20HC%20Judge%20J%20Gaurang%20Kanth%20(now%20transferred%20to%20Calcutta%20HC)%20wrote%20to%20Delhi%20JCP%20seeking%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20officers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMS0QauV6H7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMS0QauV6H7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Live%20Law%20(%40LiveLawIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1682590383065411585%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Justice%20Kanth%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20dated%20June%2012%2C%20it%20surfaced%20online%20recently%20and%20is%20being%20shared%20widely%2C%20with%20many%20accusing%20Justice%20Kanth%20of%20misusing%20his%20official%20position%20and%20also%20pointing%20to%20the%20alleged%20sense%20of%20entitlement%20found%20among%20the%20members%20of%20the%20higher%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20security%20officials%20posted%20at%20his%20residence%20%E2%80%9Cintolerable%E2%80%9D%2C%20Justice%20Kanth%20sought%20an%20action-taken%20report%20from%20Delhi%20Police%20within%20three%20working%20days.%20He%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20callousness%20in%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties%20by%20the%20said%20security%20personnel%20may%20cause%20any%20untoward%20incident%20at%20my%20residence%20and%20I%20fear%20for%20my%20security.%20Not%20manning%20the%20gate%20and%20lack%20of%20devotion%20in%20keeping%20a%20check%20on%20the%20movement%20and%20ingress%20and%20egress%20from%20the%20gate%20of%20my%20residence%20is%20intolerable.%20I%20will%20request%20you%20to%20immediately%20suspend%20the%20officers%20who%20are%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20government%20servant%20and%20carry%20out%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20regarding%20the%20aforementioned%20issue%20which%20could%20have%20been%20a%20grave%20threat%20to%20me%20and%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20life.%20An%20action%20taken%20report%20in%20this%20regard%20shall%20be%20submitted%20within%203%20(three)%20working%20days%20from%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Justice%20Kanth%20was%20last%20in%20the%20news%20when%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2FCJAR-deeply-concerned-elevation-advocate-gaurang-kant-delhi-HC-judge%5C%22%3Eserious%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20breach%20of%20trust%20and%20abuse%20of%20office%20as%20an%20advocate%E2%80%9D%20were%20levelled%20against%20him%20for%20having%20%E2%80%9Cforged%20a%20sale%20deed%20while%20being%20the%20lawyer%20and%20executor%20of%20the%20will%20of%20his%20client%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%20(CJAR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20last%20year%2C%20CJAR%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20to%20elevate%20Kanth%2C%20who%20was%20then%20an%20advocate%2C%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECJI%20asked%20judges%20to%20introspect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20of%20Justice%20Kanth%20seeking%20the%20suspension%20of%20police%20officials%20came%20to%20light%20days%20after%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20told%20judges%20to%20exercise%20judicial%20authority%20wisely%2C%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20bench%20because%20it%20%E2%80%9Csustains%20the%20credibility%20and%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20confidence%20which%20society%20has%20in%20judges%E2%80%9D.%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20on%20July%2019%20said%20there%20should%20be%20self-reflection%20and%20counselling%20within%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProtocol%20facilities%20which%20are%20made%20available%20to%20judges%20should%20not%20be%20used%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20is%20liable%20to%20result%20in%20inconvenience%20to%20others%20or%20to%20bring%20public%20criticism%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20days%20after%20another%20letter%20surfaced%20online%2C%20in%20which%20the%20registrar%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20wrote%20to%20the%20railway%20authorities%20about%20the%20train%20journey%20of%20Justice%20Gautam%20Chowdhary%2C%20during%20which%20the%20judge%20apparently%20faced%20some%20inconvenience.%20The%20letter%20had%20said%20that%20Justice%20Chowdhary%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20general%20manager%20of%20the%20North%20Central%20Railway%2C%20Prayagraj%2C%20for%20his%20poor%20experience%20on%20the%20first-class%20AC%20coach%20of%20the%20Purushotam%20Express%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EJustice%20Gautam%20Chowdhary%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAllahabadHighCourt%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AllahabadHighCourt%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20called%20for%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20erring%20officials%2C%20GRP%20personnel%20and%20pantry%20Car%20manager%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20him%20during%20his%20train%20journey%20on%20July%208%20(New%20Delhi-%20Prayagraj).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXKzXC6sdHB%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXKzXC6sdHB%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Live%20Law%20(%40LiveLawIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1681297202092834821%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20states%20that%20the%20train%20Justice%20Chowdhary%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20on%20July%208%20was%20apparently%20three%20hours%20late%20and%20there%20were%20no%20government%20railway%20police%20(GRP)%20officers%20in%20the%20coach%20to%20meet%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20requirements%20despite%20%E2%80%9Crepeated%20intimation%E2%80%9D.%20Pantry%20car%20workers%20also%20did%20not%20attend%20to%20the%20judge%20to%20provide%20refreshments%20and%20the%20pantry%20car%20manager%20did%20not%20answer%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20aforesaid%20incident%20caused%20great%20inconvenience%20and%20displeasure%20to%20His%20Lordship.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Judge%20has%20desired%20that%20the%20explanation%20may%20be%20called%20from%20the%20erring%20officials%20of%20the%20Railways%2C%20the%20GRP%20Personnel%20and%20the%20Pantry%20Car%20Manager%20pertaining%20to%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20His%20Lordship%20due%20to%20their%20conduct%20and%20dereliction%20of%20duty%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20communication%20gave%20rise%20to%20%E2%80%9Cjustifiable%20disquiet%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20Judiciary%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CProtocol%20%E2%80%98facilities%E2%80%99%20which%20are%20made%20available%20to%20Judges%20should%20not%20be%20utilised%20to%20assert%20a%20claim%20to%20privilege%20which%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20society%20or%20as%20a%20manifestation%20of%20power%20or%20authority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690381209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26180437%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-26T180423.594.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhigh-court-judge-gaurang-kanth-suspension-cops-pet-dog%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Gaurang%20Kanth%20%E2%