l2-1690375407-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel2-1690375407-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325207%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20trips%20usually%20have%206-10%20mothers%20and%20their%20children%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20full-time%20jobs%2C%20Saakshi%20and%20Nikita%20do%20all%20the%20planning%20on%20weekends%2C%20when%20they%20also%20carry%20out%20recces%20of%20new%20locations%20for%20their%20next%20adventure.%20Their%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20mothers%20and%20help%20them%20come%20out%20of%20their%20comfort%20zones%20while%20giving%20their%20children%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20giving%20birth%2C%20everyone%20tends%20to%20forget%20about%20the%20mother%20and%20focuses%20solely%20on%20the%20child.%20We%20want%20to%20prioritise%20the%20mother%20during%20the%20retreat.%20While%20we%20do%20cater%20to%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20child%2C%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20needs%20are%20not%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nikita%2C%20who%20is%20a%20full-time%20blogger%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20the%20trips%20are%20planned%20for%20two%20nights%20and%20three%20days%2C%20where%20the%20children%20can%20have%20fun%20while%20the%20mothers%20unwind.%20So%20far%2C%20their%20curated%20experiences%20have%20included%20farm-to-table%20dining%2C%20a%20mud%20bath%20in%20Goa%2C%20a%20sound%20garden%20in%20Puducherry%2C%20a%20crocodile%20bank%2C%20cooking%20classes%2C%20and%20dining%20by%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USP%20of%20their%20venture%20is%20that%20one%20of%20the%20two%20founders%20is%20always%20present%20on%20the%20trip.%20They%20personally%20visit%20and%20explore%20the%20locations%20beforehand%2C%20along%20with%20their%20families%2C%20before%20planning%20