nd%20nutrition%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20says%20that%20while%20rice%20requires%20about%204%2C500%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20kg%2C%20millets%20require%20800%20litres.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20helped%20conserve%2024%20billion%20litres%20of%20water%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fao.org%2Ffao-stories%2Farticle%2Fen%2Fc%2F1628815%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFAO%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.mohfw.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FNFHS-5_Phase-II_0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENFHS-5%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nabard.org%2Finternational-year-of-millets-2023.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENABARD%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690292980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Raju%20Bhupati%20runs%20Troo%20Good%2C%20a%20millet%20snacks%20company%20that%20aims%20to%20tackle%20malnutrition%20and%20provide%20healthier%20alternatives%20to%20regular%20snacks.%20He%20is%20on%20track%20to%20hit%20Rs%20100%20crore%20revenue%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-