0We%20want%20children%20to%20study.%E2%80%99%20With%20that%20kind%20of%20mindset%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20very%20discouraging%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20that%20attitude%20has%20markedly%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20Rai%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Anthill%20Creations%2C%20speaking%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20during%20the%20very%20first%20few%20pitches%20that%20I%20made%20for%20corporations%20for%20CSR%20funding%2C%20they%20would%20say%20%E2%80%98Our%20focus%20area%20is%20education%20and%20your%20product%20is%20not%20does%20not%20fall%20into%20that%20category%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case%20and%20there%20is%20definitely%20a%20change%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20was%20when%20Anthill%20pitched%20their%20ideas%20to%20potential%20stakeholders%2C%20people%20would%20look%20at%20the%20play%20elements%20they%20made%20out%20of%20waste%20material%20as%20something%20of%20poor%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20overcome%20all%20of%20these%20challenges%20in%20some%20way.%20At%20this%20point%20in%20time%2C%20there%20is%20very%20high%20awareness%20around%20play-based%20learning.%20All%20education%20is%20becoming%20gamified%20be%20it%20digital%20or%20non-digital.%20Everyone%20is%20talking%20about%20play-based%20learning%20today.%20So%20there%20is%20definitely%20a%20very%20high%20awareness%20that%20has%20happened%20over%20the%20past%20five%20or%20six%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20read%20more%20about%20play-based%20learning%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298277%2Fnep-early-childhood-care-and-education-play-based-learning-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2F