0was%20founded%20for%20the%20first%20time%20at%20the%20village%20level%20in%20India%20at%20Panihati%20on%2024%20March%201918.%20Bandopadhyay%20was%20the%20secretary%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20helm%20of%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20encouraged%20cleaning%20ponds%20and%20drains%20in%20the%20village%2C%20clearing%20the%20garbage%20that%20choked%20the%20lakes%20and%20distributing%20mosquito%20nets.%20This%20compelled%20other%20villages%20to%20start%20similar%20associations%20to%20curb%20the%20spread%20of%20malaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotable%20author%20Amitav%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98The%20Calcutta%20Chromosome%E2%80%99%20details%20bits%20of%20Ross%E2%80%99s%20journey%20while%20shedding%20light%20on%20his%20research%20phase.%20The%20book%20is%20said%20to%20question%20the%20boundaries%20that%20have%20been%20erected%20to%20distinguish%20truth%20from%20fiction%20and%20also%20points%20to%20how%20Bandopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20knowledge%20played%20a%20role%20in%20Ross%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20disappointment%20at%20not%20finding%20mention%20in%20Ross%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20Bandopadhyay%20went%20on%20to%20start%20The%20Panihati%20Cooperative%20Bank%20in%201927%2C%20two%20years%20after%20which%20he%20passed%20away.%20Today%2C%20as%20there%20have%20been%20several%20strides%20in%20the%20prevention%20and%20cure%20of%20malaria%2C%20we%20remain%20indebted%20to%20Kishori%20Mohan%20Bandyopadhyay%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303410%2Firish-teacher-sister-nivedita-cared-for-poor-fought-plague-and-british-rule-in-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etremendous%20contribution%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%